    <node id="&quot;IMAGE_16&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORI_IMG"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The image displays a small, pixelated icon, predominantly in shades of gray and white. It features a circular shape with a thick black outline, enclosing a white interior. Inside this white circle, there are two distinct, vertically oriented black figures. The figure on the left is thinner and appears to be a stylized representation of a fork, while the figure on the right is slightly wider and resembles a knife. Both figures are simple, linear forms. The overall impression is that of a universal symbol, likely indicating a dining facility or food service."</data>
