    <node id="&quot;IMAGE_12&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORI_IMG"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The image displays a single, prominent character, which is the uppercase Greek letter Delta (Δ). The character is rendered in a grayscale or metallic-looking texture, giving it a somewhat three-dimensional and slightly reflective appearance. It is set against a dark, possibly black, background, which provides strong contrast and makes the white/gray character stand out clearly. The symbol itself is a triangle with its base at the bottom and its apex pointing upwards, characteristic of the Delta symbol. The edges of the symbol appear somewhat blurred or softened, suggesting a slight glow or a low-resolution rendering."</data>
