    <node id="&quot;IMAGE_11&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORI_IMG"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The image displays a simple, dark gray, almost black, rounded rectangular shape, acting as a container or background for a logo. Inside this dark shape, two prominent capital letters, 'FS', are centrally positioned. These letters are rendered in a lighter shade of gray, appearing metallic or silver, with a subtle gradient that gives them a slightly three-dimensional or embossed effect. The letters are sans-serif and bold, standing out against the darker background. The overall icon is set against a plain white background, making the 'FS' logo the sole focus of the image."</data>
