    <node id="&quot;IMAGE_7&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORI_IMG"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The image is a small, monochrome, pixelated graphic featuring the letters "FS". The letters are rendered in a bold, blocky, sans-serif font, appearing in a light gray or white color against a dark gray or black background. The letters "F" and "S" are clearly distinguishable, with the "F" having a strong vertical stem and two horizontal bars, and the "S" forming a characteristic curved shape. The edges of both the letters and the background show visible pixelation, giving the graphic a distinct low-resolution or retro digital aesthetic. The overall shape of the graphic is rectangular, and the letters are centrally placed within this frame. It appears to be an icon, a logo, or a small graphic identifier."</data>
