      <data key="d0">"IMG"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The category of this image feature block is 'person'. The entity features are as follows:Person Features:- **Gender:** Appears to be male.- **Skin color:** Indiscernible due to the grayscale and low resolution of the image.- **Hairstyle:** Short, dark hair, possibly styled with a fringe or slightly messy over the forehead.- **Facial features:**    - **Eyes:** Wearing glasses with what appear to be rectangular or slightly rounded frames. The eyes themselves are not clearly visible.    - **Nose:** Visible, but details are obscured by low resolution.    - **Mouth:** Appears to be closed, with a hint of a slight smile or neutral expression.- **Expression:** Seems to have a neutral to slightly positive or thoughtful expression.- **Age:** Appears to be an adult, possibly young to middle-aged.- **Clothing:** Only a very small portion of what might be a collar or shoulder of a shirt is visible on the right side, making specific clothing details impossible to determine.- **Accessories:** Clearly wearing glasses.- **Posture:** The head is slightly tilted to the left (from the viewer's perspective), and the person is looking generally towards the viewer. The image captures a headshot.Overall, the person appears to be looking directly or slightly off-camera, wearing glasses, with a somewhat indistinct facial expression due to the image's quality."</data>
      <data key="d2">test_runs/test_mmrag_working\images\image_5.jpg</data>
