    <node id="&quot;INDOOR EXHIBIT HALL&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
      <data key="d1">"An interior space, likely a museum or science center, characterized by artificial lighting and other structural elements in the background, serving as the setting for the interactive sphere."</data>
